<p>Dear teacher,<br><br>In 4 weeks, an Ans exam will take place for @{items('Apply_to_each_-_send_e-mails')?['Vaktitel']} (@{items('Apply_to_each_-_send_e-mails')?['Vakcode']}). Log in to Ans at <a href="https://ans.uva.nl">ans.uva.nl</a>.<br><br><strong>How do I get started?</strong><br>Because Ans is a brand new application, we strongly recommend <a href="https://outlook.office365.com/book/ICTOSocialSciences@Amsuni.onmicrosoft.com/">booking an (online) appointment with the ICTO team</a>. During the appointment, we'll walk you through Ans and prepare your first exam together. If you desire, we can also get started on building a lasting question bank for your couse. Would you rather get started yourself? Have a look at our instructions <a href="https://canvas.uva.nl/courses/45162/pages/tools-ans-quickstart">here</a>. Moreover, we encourage you to <a href="https://canvas.uva.nl/courses/45228">share this FAQ about digital examination</a> with students. This page also shows students how to take a practice test in Ans to get familiar with the new system.<br><br><strong>Exam information:</strong></p>
